  "keyFeatures": [
    "66+ JSDoc linting rules for ESLint",
    "Recommended preset configs for JavaScript, TypeScript, and TSDoc",
    "Flat config (ESLint v9+) and classic eslintrc support",
    "Auto-fixable rules for consistent formatting",
    "TypeScript-aware rules and type validation",
    "Processor for linting @example code blocks",
    "Granular rule subsets: contents, logical, requirements, stylistic",
    "Structured tag configuration and alias preferences"
